_sText: A map I made while listening to a 7 hour trance playlist through iTunes. Anti-aliasing and Bloom/HDR is recommended, but not essential. Merge the maps folder with the maps folder in your cstrike folder. _____ I noticed there isn't much cover in the center of the map (if you are playing with guns, not knifes that is). I'll improve upon it and make more cover points in V2. This isn't nearly my best effort, but it's a theme for a map I've really wanted to make! I'll probably make one not as seizure inducing. ______________________

This map and all their files are too big for the default MAX DOWNLOAD SIZE!
                       Use this command so players can download every file needed for this map 
                       
                       net_maxfilesize 45 
                       
                       Without this command changed to 45, people will download all the resources EXCEPT the .BSP 
                       and they will get an error message like "fy_simpsons_house_css.bsp not found".
                       -->If your server BZIPs the maps you're ok, but make sure you test it first.

Made by: Gam£m0nK£Y

This is a map I made because a clan asked me to remake the original fy_shotgun. There are a few things you should note, camping by the ramps to the basement or behind the boxes will result in damage taken by the camper.  It is meant to keep the game moving and free of campers as it is supposed to be very fast paced.

**EDIT: NEW VERSION UPDATED!**

The newest and funnest shotgun map is here FY_SHOTGUN_BOXES this map spawns you in an arena stlye map inside an inclosed box you must shoot your way out to find where you are. You might be spawned right next to your enemy so be careful. The map has auto shotguns stored in the midlee section on top but you need to be the first to get there. It also has gernades for the angry people who play This map is loads of fun HAVE FUN GAMMING.
